    {
      "bookmarkId": "390215_1_2908-2984",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2908-2984",
      "markText": "他以此为己任，努力将自己塑造好；从学识、思想、能力到身体，力求向上，时有变易；既动笔又看书，每天写日记；生活极有规律，读书问难、锻炼身体，都按计划行事。",
      "totalCount": 88,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=390215&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2908&rangeEnd=2984",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92a32bf055f44792a170ec3?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2908&rangeEnd=2984"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "390215_1_12638-12727",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "12638-12727",
      "markText": "他的实践家的身份超过理论家的身份；他总是用自己的行动来证实自己的设想，用革命的实践来证实革命的理论，即“真理的标准只能是社会的实践”（《实践论》），从而使两者不断发展，永远前进。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=390215&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=12638&rangeEnd=12727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92a32bf055f44792a170ec3?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=12638&rangeEnd=12727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "390215_12_9642-9700",
